{"data":[{"date":"10:15 19/08","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c hay bu\u00f4ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng nhau \u1edf m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean BXH. C\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec theo lu\u1eadt, c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1ea5t hay nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi quan tr\u1ecdng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, theo c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan, Qatar), ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E (Bahrain, Kyrgyzstan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3ng F (Iran, Saudi Arabia hay Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Malaysia v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eeda th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Olympic Malaysia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0110N\u00c1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Malaysia. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ong Kim Swee t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1edd toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch tr\u00ean, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u thay cho V\u0103n Thanh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n Thanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 hay bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Goc-nhin-Olympic-Viet-Nam-da-hay-buong-tran-gap-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u00f9ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Song c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng hay \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng trong.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Khi m\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Thanh hay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n th\u00ec s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103n HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ee3i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. C\u1ea3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eeba khao kh\u00e1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia-168-194784.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan-168-194746.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194745.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194711.html\">Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u00e1ch chia b\u1ea3ng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5652","checkdouble":"194794"},{"date":"11:01 19/08","title":"Sarri gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao Chelsea b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Arsenal v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u1edf th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/sarri-giai-thich-vi-sao-chelsea-bi-loi-nguoc-dong-trong-hiep-mot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal derby London</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn hai b\u00e0n ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh tan th\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng b\u1ed1n ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Maurizio Sarri vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd sau tr\u1eadn derby London k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf: \u201cTh\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f3.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n ra qu\u00e1 xa v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 15 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i pressing \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7, ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn 4-5 l\u1ea7n s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chao \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb Arsenal.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u00e1u \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn St. James\u2019 Park l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Newcastle.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Video tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5651","checkdouble":"194795"},{"date":"11:25 19/08","title":"Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh De Gea c\u00f3 gi\u00e1... 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/mourinho-khang-dinh-de-gea-co-gia-0-dong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng ra \u0111i khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau ba n\u0103m, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man Utd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm \u00e2u lo v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i David De Gea, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Chelsea ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00ec Kepa Arrizabalanga. N\u00f3i chung, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00ean v\u1ecb v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ebf n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c De Gea ra \u0111i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/mourinho-khang-dinh-de-gea-co-gia-0-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Man Utd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c anh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn cho to\u00e0n Old Trafford theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 h\u00f3m h\u1ec9nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta qu\u00ean th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Gi\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a David r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1edbt gi\u00e1 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho ai h\u1ebft, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 CLB, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho MU. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea3 ba b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng: B\u1ed1n th\u1eadp ni\u00ean b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f3a m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5650","checkdouble":"194796"},{"date":"11:51 19/08","title":"Arsenal thua \u0111au, Emery v\u1eabn vui v\u00ec Ozil... bi\u1ebft nghe l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-dau-emery-van-vui-vi-ozil-biet-nghe-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV x\u1ee9 Basque h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn derby London g\u1eb7p Chelsea.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng san b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t hai b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm t\u1ea1o ra, Arsenal cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eafng tay ra v\u1ec1 khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Alonso l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac trong th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u1edf derby London n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-chelsea-vs-arsenal-32-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194768.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Ozil tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Ozil tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-dau-emery-van-vui-vi-ozil-biet-nghe-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Ozil tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Emery c\u00f3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ozil v\u1ec1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cH\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i vui v\u00ec nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00f3 \u0111ang b\u1ecb Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda sau.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea, Arsenal \u0111ang ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf Premier League nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London kh\u00e1c khi Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian-172-194779.html\">Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5649","checkdouble":"194797"},{"date":"07:25 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; khi gi\u1eef l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +5 (b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt song t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1ea3ng D do h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 fair-play. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec sau 90 ph\u00fat, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nhat-Ban-(16h00-ngay-198)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, d\u00f9 th\u1eafng, h\u00f2a hay b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i th\u00ec \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo 99% kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 16 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng nh\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Uzbekistan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh 1 su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u00ec nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng &ldquo;bu\u00f4ng&rdquo; tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn chi\u1ec1u nay nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang D ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng D ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bang-D-ASIAD.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm vinh quang t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n &ndash; khi danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb U21 tham d\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ecd s\u00e1t v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tokyo 2020, k\u1ef3 th\u1ebf v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng toan t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nhat Ban\" title=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-pakistan-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 Thebault Yamaguchi v\u00e0 Tatsuya Ito. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21, song ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eeb c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110TQG. Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 l\u1ea7n so t\u00e0i cao th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf to\u00e0n thua, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mang t\u00ednh danh d\u1ef1.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sau l\u00fac n\u00e0y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng; Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, V\u0103n Thanh; \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ryosuke Kojima; Takahiro Yanagi; Teruki Hara; Honoya Shoji; Taiyo Koga; So Fujitani; Itsuki Urata; Koji Miyoshi; Tsukasa Morishima; Kyosuke Tagawa; Ren Komatsu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: 0-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5648","checkdouble":"194784"},{"date":"07:10 19/08","title":"Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Alaves, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Barcelona gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1eadp n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho La Liga.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19, Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Barcelona \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Alaves v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-0. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6000 t\u1ea1i La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6000 t\u1ea1i La Liga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6000 t\u1ea1i La Liga.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Barca, Messi c\u00f2n l\u1eadp c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000 t\u1ea1i La Liga. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Messi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00f2n th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh \"Leo\" ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00f2n 5.000 cho La Liga v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u m\u1ed1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho La Liga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Messi g\u1ed3m Manuel Parera (1 - 1929), Marcos Aurelio (1.000 - 1950), Pedro Tomas Zaballa (2.000 - 1964), Quini (3.000 - 1982), Guillermo Amor (4.000 - 1996).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6.4% trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 6.000 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i La Liga, Lionel Messi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6.4% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 15 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i La Liga trong th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 21.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi-180-194656.html\">Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu-184-194514.html\">Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-boca-juniors-23h15-ngay-158-joan-gamper-372-194556.html\">Barca 3-0 Boca Juniors: C\u00fap Joan Gamper ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5647","checkdouble":"194781"},{"date":"07:48 19/08","title":"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Philippe Coutinho - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \"ba sao\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.</h2><h2>B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lionel Messi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh &quot;Leo&quot; l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn khung g\u1ed7 gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nhan xet bat ngo ve Lionel Messi sau tran thang Alaves.\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &quot;Messi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Barca chia s\u1ebb ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Levante khi b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f2n c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Coutinho. Nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Arthur v\u00e0 Vidal ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-barca-vs-alaves-30-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194780.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-0 Alaves (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi-180-194656.html\">Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5646","checkdouble":"194785"},{"date":"08:31 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 20/8): Barca g\u1ecdi, Real s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-getafe-3h15-ngay-208-barca-goi-real-se-tra-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves, CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Getafe kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Bernabeu &ndash; tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Th\u1eadt may, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung Getafe.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 208) Barca g\u1ecdi, Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 208) Barca g\u1ecdi, Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Nhan-dinh-Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-(3h15-ngay-208)-Barca-goi,-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Getafe</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Real nh\u01b0ng CLB Getafe ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec v\u1edbi Los Blancos \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o, t\u1eeb b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn danh ti\u1ebfng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 26 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Geta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n Real, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Getafe. C\u00f2n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008/09 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Getafe \u0111\u00e3 9 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Los Blancos v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 9 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Getafe, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 khi m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1edd Lopetegui<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Getafe v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Real. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u00edt \u1ecfi t\u1ea1i Real, vi\u1ec7c Lopetegui c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n La Liga s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui noi cung sau tran thua Atletico Madrid.\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn sau khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8 chung cu\u1ed9c. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Real, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Getafe kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0&nbsp; David Soria, Vitorino Antunes, Ignasi Miquel v\u00e0 Nemanja Maksimovic.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 Cristiano Ronaldo sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Los Blancos v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &lsquo;con m\u1ed3i ngon&rsquo; c\u1ee7a Los Blancos trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Real Madrid h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Getafe v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lopetegui \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 La Liga s\u1ebd v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid: \u00c1lvaro Odriozola, Jes\u00fas Vallejo (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe: Markel Bergara (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Djen\u00e9 Dakonam (kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid (4-3-3): Navas; Ramos, Varane, Carvajal, Marcelo; Casemiro, Isco, Kroos; Bale, Asensio, Benzema.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe (4-4-2): Soria; Gonzalez, Dakoman, Suarez, Antunes; Maksimovic, Portillo, Ndiaye; Molina, Rodriguez.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n&nbsp;Real Madrid vs Getafe: 2-1.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-180-194621.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-180-194621.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB Real Madrid trong su\u1ed1t 18 n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\">S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018</span><br>\r\nSau bi\u1ebft bao n\u1ed7i \u0111au tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, Atletico Madrid cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Atletico trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5645","checkdouble":"194788"},{"date":"07:17 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield (19h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8): \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam ba \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c n\u1eefa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Etihad ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League, Manchester City kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi v\u1eabn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng tr\u1ea3i qua ba th\u00e1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hai b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u01a1i x\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal. Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh r\u1ed3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Man City c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 n\u00e9t \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng Nicolas Otamendi, David Silva hay c\u1ea3 Kevin De Bruyne, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn b\u0103ng b\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ba th\u00e1ng xem ra kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eb7n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00eanh thang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i mang t\u00ean Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng De Bruyne, Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ef5 ng\u00e3, th\u1ebf n\u00ean nh\u1eefng Huddersfield hay Wolverhampton, Newcastle, Fulham, Cardiff, Brighton s\u1eafp t\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 vua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Bernardo Silva nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne, hay t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c Riyad Mahrez, c\u1ea3 Benjamin Mendy v\u00e0 Aymeric Laporte c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling tran Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"Sterling tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Du-am-Arsenal-0-2-Man-City-Sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-Anh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Etihad c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town c\u00f3 ch\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e0ng \u00edt b\u00e0n thua c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i, trong khi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3, Huddersfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 David Wagner.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/10/DcyGxr0W4AA33Sj.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\">Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Huddersfield: H\u00e3y c\u1ee9 tin \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng bao ng\u1edd ng\u1eebng!</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Chelsea ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Stamford Bridge, Huddersfield tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ef1c cho ri\u00eang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ef1a trung l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m Etihad g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00ednh Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady n\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 vua ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Man-City-vs-Huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man City (4-3-3): 31. Ederson; 2. Walker \u2013 5. Stones \u2013 14. Laporte \u2013 22. Mendy; 8. Gundogan \u2013 25. Fernandinho \u2013 20. Bernardo; 26. Mahrez \u2013 33. Jesus \u2013 7. Sterling<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huddersfield (4-2-3-1): 12. Hamer; 33. Hadergjonaj \u2013 26. Schindler \u2013 5. Kongolo \u2013 15. Lowe; 10. Mooy \u2013 6. Hogg; 17. Van La Parra \u2013 21. Pritchard \u2013 11. Diakhaby; 24. Mounie<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield: 4-0<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5644","checkdouble":"194783"},{"date":"08:34 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-brighton-vs-man-utd-22h00-ngay-198-cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 Old Trafford \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Manchester United b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 t\u1eeb chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u00e0 r\u1ed1i ren \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 xoay quanh Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn t\u1eeb ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Paul Pogba.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Brighton vs Man Utd\" title=\"Preview Brighton vs Man Utd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Preview-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City gi\u00fap Man Utd tr\u00fat b\u1ecf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eefng tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, v\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft tinh th\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU khi m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, h\u1ecd cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi phong \u0111\u1ed9, khi Pogba v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo tay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong khi Luke Shaw c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh Pogba l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u00f3a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u1ee1m \u1edd kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mourinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Falmer, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ra ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0o v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n r\u1eddi mi\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nam, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 ba t\u00e2n binh Premier League trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd-(22h00-ngay-198)-Cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ni\u1ec1m tin c\u0169ng c\u00e0ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n khi tr\u00f4ng sang t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, Brighton g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 thay m\u00e1u to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi chia tay \u0111\u1ebfn 28 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eafn b\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n sau khi h\u1ebft th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho 16 t\u00e2n binh khao kh\u00e1t th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Watford trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u00e8 v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t qua s\u00e1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brighton ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Cho n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Falmer trong m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch MU t\u1ed1i nay c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd-(22h00-ngay-198)-Cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brighton (4-4-1-1): 1. Ryan; 22. Montoya \u2013 4. Duffy \u2013 5. Dunk \u2013 30. Bernardo; 16. Jahanbakhsh \u2013 6. Stephens \u2013 8. Bissouma \u2013 20. March; 13. Gross \u2013 17. Murray<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd (4-3-3): 1. De Gea; 18. Young \u2013 3. Bailly \u2013 2. Lindelof \u2013 23. Shaw; 17. Fred \u2013 15. Pereira \u2013 6. Pogba; 8. Mata \u2013 9. Lukaku \u2013 7. Sanchez<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU: 1-2<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5643","checkdouble":"194787"},{"date":"03:32 19/08","title":"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Allegri cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A d\u00f9 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Juve v\u00e0 Chievo v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Real v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng CR7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u00e0n Serie A. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Allegri v\u1eabn khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo d\u00f9 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRonaldo c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong v\u00f2ng 7 ng\u00e0y qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ronaldo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Sorrentino \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0i pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Ronaldo h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chievo ch\u1ec9 sau 3 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n sau \u0111\u00f3. May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mattia Bani v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Federico Bernardeschi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\">Chievo 2-3 Juventus: Ronaldo im \u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-juve-chia-tay-marchisio-sau-25-nam-gan-bo-176-194689.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5642","checkdouble":"194772"},{"date":"01:37 19/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Guingamp 1-3 PSG (V\u00f2ng 2 Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/video-tong-hop-guingamp-13-psg-vong-2-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, PSG \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1.</h2><h2>PSG \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, PSG \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1.</h2>\r\nB\u00c0N TH\u1eaeNG<br>\r\nGuingamp: Nolan Roux (20')<br>\r\nPSG: Neymar (pen, 53'), Mbappe (82, 90')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp, HLV Thomas Tuchel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung v\u00e0o ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Edinson Cavani hay Mbappe. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, PSG \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, PSG c\u00f2n su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf ph\u00fat 13 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Buffon v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn. B\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nolan Roux \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Buffon v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn x\u00e0 ngang. D\u00f9 Roux \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 20, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Colin Dagba c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 Marcus Regis Coco \u0111o\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m. Coco chuy\u1ec1n cho Roux d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Guingamp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, HLV Tuchel bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tung qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u. Ph\u00fat 53, Neymar t\u1ef1 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho PSG. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Guingamp c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ec PSG s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t Mbappe thi\u00ean t\u00e0i. V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 2 b\u00e0n cho PSG \u1edf ph\u00fat 82 v\u00e0 90 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Tuchel l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau 2 tr\u1eadn, PSG v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u Ligue 1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Guingamp \u0111ang t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 18 sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n<br>\r\nGuingamp: Johnsson; Ikoko, Kerbrat, Eboa, Rebocho; Didot (Sorbon 81'), Blas, Coco, Benezet (Rodelin 66'), Thuram (Salibur 75'); Roux<br>\r\nPSG: Buffon; Dagba, Marquinhos, Silva, Meunier; Bernede (Lo Celso 80'), Rabiot, Nkunku (Diaby 74'); Neymar, Di Maria, Weah (Mbappe 46')<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5641","checkdouble":"194767"},{"date":"19:59 18/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8: Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-188-pogba-duoc-thuong-lon-neu-tu-choi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8.</h2><h2>Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8: Pogba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3.4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0 3.4 b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Man United v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Negredo s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Monaco</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;T\u1edd RMC Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Negredo \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Monaco t\u1eeb Besiktas. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin tr\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Gonalons ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Sevilla</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd La Gazzetta dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Maxime Gonalons \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma cho ph\u00e9p gia nh\u1eadp Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<h2>Marchisio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin tr\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Claudio Marchisio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t Buffon gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain sau khi r\u1eddi Juventus. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Marchisio \u0111ang t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay th\u00e0nh Turin. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng &ldquo;Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed&rdquo; s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn MLS nh\u01b0ng PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi anh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Monaco theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd France Football \u0111\u01b0a tin Monaco \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida t\u1eeb Besiktas. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Croatia. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Monaco s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nGalatasaray nh\u1eafm sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AMK kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Galatasaray \u0111ang nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Welbeck. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Emirates. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea1o tay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf Champions League. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Welbeck kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-178-cuu-sao-psg-khuyen-neymar-toi-real-184-194694.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/8: C\u1ef1u sao PSG khuy\u00ean Neymar t\u1edbi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-178-barca-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-hau-ve-tiem-nang-184-194638.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8: Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5640","checkdouble":"194759"}]}